newsitem.title: USA: Roosevelt Financial Q3 oper net down.
newsitem.headline: Roosevelt Financial Q3 oper net down.

text.p: (All Data Above 000s Except Per Share Numbers)

NOTE: Q3 1996 operating earnings exclude $17.8 million, or $0.38 a share charge to recapitalize Savings Association Insurance Fund. Including the SAIF charge and one-time charges connected with early extinguishment of debt, the company had net loss of $548,000, or $0.01 a share, in the quarter.
